Ian Nepomniachtchi vs Pavel Anisimov
FIDE Online World Corporate Championship | East E
20.2. 2021.
French, Rubinstein, Capablanca line (C10)

1. e4 e6 2. d4 d5 3. Nc3 dxe4 4. Nxe4 Nd7 5. Nf3 Ngf6 6. Nxf6+ Nxf6 7. Ne5 Nd7 8. Nc4 Nf6 9. Bf4 Be7 10. Be5 O-O 11. Bd3 b5 12. Ne3 c5 13. Qf3 cxd4 14. O-O-O Qa5 15. Bxd4 Ba6 16. Ng4 Nxg4 17. Qxg4 g6 18. Kb1 b4 19. Bxa6 Qxa6 20. h4 h5 21. Qf4 Qb5 22. g4 Rad8 23. Qh6 e5 24. gxh5 Rxd4 25. hxg6 Rxd1+ 26. Rxd1 fxg6 27. Qxg6+ Kh8 28. Rg1

The FIDE Online World Corporate Championship | East A is a 6-round Swiss tournament taking place from February 19-20 on chess.com. The winning team qualifies along with the winners of 7 other groups for the knockout on February 21.

Each team can feature one invited player, must have no more than one BELOW 2500 rated player and must include a female player. Players receive 10 minutes for the entire game, plus a 2-second increment starting from move one. Official website: worldcorporate.fide.com
